data.description: ***$5,000 lender credit available***  Welcome to 5691 Red Ridge Lane, an exquisite 3-bedroom, 4-bathroom townhome in the heart of West Valley City, UT. Built in 2017, this modern gem offers a seamless blend of style and comfort. The meticulously designed interior boasts a spacious layout, with the main floor featuring a sleek kitchen, a cozy living area, and a guest bathroom. The finished basement provides versatility, ideal for a home office or entertainment haven. Park with ease in the attached 2-car garage. With its prime location, close to schools, parks, and shopping, this townhome presents an unmissable opportunity for a vibrant and convenient lifestyle. Experience contemporary living at its finest at 5691 Red Ridge Lane.
